title: Electric Blue Elephant - Food Truck
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, American, Pizza, Organic, Take-out only
description: Mobile kitchen serving Reno and North Lake Tahoe. Food is gluten-free, vegetarian and vegan (uses honey). Offers a small menu that changes and makes new twists on old favorites: grilled cheese, sushi, pizza, sandwiches, soups, salads, pies and brownies.
